-- Emaar Economic City, Al Rajhi Sign 30-Year Lease, Al Bayan Says
-- B y   Z a i n a b   F a t t a h
-- 2012-02-16T07:04:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-16/emaar-economic-city-al-rajhi-sign-30-year-lease-al-bayan-says.html
Emaar Economic City (EMAAR) , a unit of
Dubai’s  Emaar Properties PJSC (EMAAR) , signed a 30-year lease agreement
with Al Rajhi Heavy Industries for 4 million square meters of
land,  Al Bayan  reported, citing Fahd Al Rasheed, Emaar Economic
City’s managing director.  Al Rajhi will invest 15 billion dirhams ($4.1 billion) to
create an industrial complex, which is scheduled to start
production by the fourth quarter of 2015, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zainab Fattah in Dubai at 
